Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh, I wanna go on a date with Iyona-chan so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna, wanna! \NI so wanna go on a date...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The torments of love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru is {\i1}that{\i0} age, after all. {/in the right age}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:02:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Hey! That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it, you got a Five-pointed Pleaseal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Five-pointed Pleaseal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A Five-pointed Pleaseal that'd make only one wish come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But do take care, Honmaru. {/you should excercise caution}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you abuse the wish to offend or hurt others, \Nit'll catch up to you later. {/return to yourself}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to use that wish for peace and happiness then, alright? {/Try to make a wish that'd serve \Nto promote peace and happiness as much as possible, okay?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Sister Ria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, hurry up and speak your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,O Lord, o Great Buddha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Iyona-chan more than anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us have a date in the park today. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, hurry up to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sister Ria!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto! We're going out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto, I need a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to create the right mood for me and Iyona-chan today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave that to me!
