Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, did Iyona-chan really come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Taruruuto, as agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, as agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:04:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ninomaru. {not in manga neither in wiki, guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wishing you a wonderful morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, Iyona-chan is cuter than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, were you busy with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was reading a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought to myself, "What a pleasant day". \NThen, somehow, before I knew it, my feet took me here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So it worked? {/after all?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I sit here? {/Is this seat vacant?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't Ria's magic amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, where is Taru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto is on a date with Mimora-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Me here. But be hush about it.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't Taru-chan and Mimora-chan lucky \Nto be getting along so well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even her laugh is beyond cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it feels like the spring's warmth is arriving again, \Nbut only around us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good, Honmaru. Right atmosphere. {/feeling/mood}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Iyona-chan, what book are you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This? A book called Earth's Ecosystem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ecosystem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Never expected less from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Great books you're reading there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I sure wonder what kind of stuff is written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still just a kid, so I don't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:07:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This book is about the trees, grass, and flowers \Nthat surround us from all sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, trees bathe in sunlight \Nand perform photosynthesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They breathe in carbon dioxide, \Nthen exhale oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As for us, we breathe in that oxygen \Nand exhale carbon dioxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Which, in turn, is consumed by trees again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nurtured and blessed by the sun, the trees and grass \Ngrow big enough. And then, animals eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But before long, those animals would also die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Those animals return to the earth, \Nfrom which vegetation is born anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,On our planet, this cycle comes full circle, \Ngoes on around and around, spreading life all-round. {(after) bouncing around from one place to the next}{intentional convoluted wording}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This harmonious flow of living organisms is the circle of life, \Nwhich constitutes the essence of our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I get it now! \NSince it goes on around and around, it forms a circular cycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How peculiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That text was so difficult, I didn't understand a word of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, if you ponder seriously on the carbon cycle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! {g, could be yes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Honmaru mouth-flaps, trying to say something. {/gaping; repeatedly opening and closing (one's mouth); gasping​}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Forehead hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Head! It's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bright."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ma!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gic."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Head, bright, ma, gic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Magic for making you bright-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Turbohead-kun. \NHelps increase the speed at which your head operates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Taruruuto's magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of book should I... {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's the kind of books you're into? {/reading}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Admittedly, our human species has been hitherto single-minded in our pursuit of self-preservation.  {確かに今まで僕ら人間は個の存在ばかりに目を向けていて}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, little heed \Ndid we spare to the ecosystem as a whole. {生態系全体を考えた行動をとっていなかったね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan seems stupefied by my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ergo the cataclysmic crisis we had to face as of recently;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that is, each and every organic system \Ncollapsing all around our Blue Planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mood is perfect between Honmaru and Iyona. \NBut I gotta try even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All life forms are afflicted by that rapacious, wanton slaughter, \Nnot to mention the wars waged amongst humanity.  {さまざまな生命に対しての欲圧や殺害人間同士の戦争 }
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, pollution and radioactive contamination. {そして公害や放射能汚染}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To contend post-haste with those challenges, we need \Nto advocate for our coexistence with the flora and fauna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Overhead Falleaves. \NWould help boost the mood even more. {no clue, not in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a world for just the two of them. \NMood is excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A success! Iyona-chan is completely entranced by my words!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, we need to find our unison with the universe, \Nand reach for it in our heart of hearts. {In other words, we pursue the oneness of the universe within ourselves.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That may well be our fated mission, as humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even this tiny fallen leaf
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is a part of the process that supports our big earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, you're truly amazing. \NIt's as if you're knowledgeable about everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I wouldn't go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was enthralled listening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Overhead Falleaves fall-fall, fall there, fall here. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dragonfly. Red dragonfly!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan! Iyona-chan, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what had just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A mystery indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Actually, Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, would you like to ride a boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taru! You're overdoing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Me overdid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Mood-upping Gramophone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Creates romantic atmosphere between two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So far so good, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, now we'll make Iyona stick to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:31.23,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H8D7F45&\3c&HA9C3BD&}Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Fangust-kun. {風々うちわくん - yes, I couldn't come up with a single portmanteau word combining wind and fan}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can cause all kinds of wind to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gro-ro-ro-row!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:37.28,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(140,200)\c&H8D7F45&\3c&HA9C3BD&}Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be Taru's doing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be alright, Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Iyona-chan's skin is so soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And such a sweet smell when she's close! {no clue what's first word, g}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona and Honmaru hugging tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright now. The storm has settled, Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I lost my composure. {to be upset; to lose one's composure; to lose self-control; to go to pieces; to be shaken up; to break down; to be flustered; to blow one's cool}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.91,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, coming from a girl, that was rather cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Said it! My head is still turbocharged! \NThat's Turbohead-kun for you! {lit: working tirelessly; working hard​ spinning}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're scared, \Ndon't hesitate to jump on my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I just keep those killer lines coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That line sounds a bit precocious for your age, \NHonmaru-kun. {actually says "NOT to be precocious; to be mature for one's age; to seem grown-up; to seem mature" so unsure, maybe the meaning is opposite}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I look at you and they roll off the tongue naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru doing well so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll be helping you from invisibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Erase, erase, erase, erase.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"The long sobs of the violins of autumn\NWound my heart with a monotonous languor."{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chanson_d%27automne - apparently they used some shitty japanese translation that deviates a lot from this text}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That poem by Verlaine is sublime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, you're much more than meets the eye. \NYou're actually quite the romanticist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Iyona-chan, what a cute smile you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Me find myself in trouble... {御座る}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't come near! Shoo! Shoo! Oh, you... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninomaru? Ninomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's muster up the courage and go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninomaru! {sounds like urameru or something but idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's wrong, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That doggie is getting in the way. Getting in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, let me deal with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Era-ra-ra-rase!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's more getting in the way! \NNot romantic at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll deal with that too! {g}
