Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Era-ra-ra-ra-ra-rase!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better. Much, much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How about some candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Candy! Anyone want to have some candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, this park is full of noisy people! \NYou'll be getting in the way! I'll erase everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Already, it's autumn... {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks ominously empty today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So it would seem, Jabao-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What? In the way? {actually means his surname, jaba}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Jabao-san, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo, where did you go yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Korekiyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "here"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pitcher swings at the third pitch! {no idea but assuming the viewers don't know the rules either}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he decide on a forkball?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike! Batter out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, time for some more closeness with Iyona. {/make ... hug/stick to more}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gro-ro-ro-row!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it this way. {hope he means this}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for finishing touches. \NI'll use this - Yahook up with me-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When this arrow pierces someone's heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,they fall in love with the person in the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take any chances with this, \Nso I'll shoot them all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Takoyaki stall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, I brought yours too. {assumed tottekita but really unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I love more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you're so handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You all think you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. How about... {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Serious. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thoughtful. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Careless. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, girls, you're so troublesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Ah, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, Iyona is walking away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do, what to do, what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, can you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The voice of autumn
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this kid? {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,None of the arrows pierced the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the magic wore off in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we appreciate this big blue sky? {/high}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we stare into this blue yonder together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are to be hitting on our women? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not kidding, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You little!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, don't get even close to our women!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, Honmaru, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, don't get up! Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My little idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Autumn day, autumn sky, autumn wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona's laps as a pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru oh-so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, what's the matter? \NAnother special training?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm going to the mountains with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm coming too. \NTrust me with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this time I want to try out my own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So just wait at home, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Honmaru, you don't want to bring me along? {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, a Tearful Decision. {本丸、涙の決心}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.33,0:23:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, come back soon!
